lead_paragraph: Prosecutors are reviewing a police file as they decide whether to charge Buffalo Bills running back LeSean McCoy in a Philadelphia nightclub brawl that left two off-duty police officers injured.

headline.print_headline: Prosecutors Weigh Charges Against LeSean McCoy in Club Brawl
